{"$category":"crawled","mainimg":"http://file21.mafengwo.net/M00/91/E7/wKgB3FH_RjSANtyaAAMm4TgCvLc23.book.w230.jpeg","addname":"鸡鸣驿","tags":"<div class=\"clear\"></div>","abstracts":"<p><strong>简介</strong> 也许很多人对鸡鸣驿很陌生，但你一定记得《大话西游》最后一幕那黄沙漫天的城楼——黄沙漫天，橘红的夕阳，泛着霞光，凌乱在那座古老的城楼上，墙头边，至尊宝做了一件他五百年前应该做却没有做的事情，只可惜爱已逝。这一段曾经感动了无数人。鸡鸣驿城位于河北省怀来县鸡鸣驿乡鸡鸣驿村，最初是一个明朝驿站。城里精心雕琢的青砖瓦房，古老的土砌房屋，经受了百年风沙的侵袭，已经变得破败斑驳，而从这坍圮和古老之中仍可一窥当年的风貌。中心的驿署区、西北区的马号，东北区的驿仓，城南的傍城驿道，还有城内的商店、民居都一一等你去发现它尘封的历史。</p>","imgs":"<li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"0\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file21.mafengwo.net/M00/91/E7/wKgB3FH_RjSANtyaAAMm4TgCvLc23.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"1\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file21.mafengwo.net/M00/91/E9/wKgB3FH_RjWANCFhAAVhg86iuWI35.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"2\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file20.mafengwo.net/M00/91/EA/wKgB3FH_RjeAemN-AAVQZDwETCQ56.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" height=\"195\">\n                        <span>点击<br>预览</span>\n                    </a>\n                </li>\n                            <li class=\"scroll-content-item\">\n                    <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"on_fous preview_btn\" data-paper_num=\"3\">\n                        <img src=\"http://file20.mafengwo.net/M00/91/EA/wKgB3FH_RjiACA3MAAVkl4t4Vkk22.book.w130.jpeg\" width=\"138\" hei